name: The Unknown
description: Sometimes, the most terrifying things in the cosmos come not from the farthest reaches, but from within. Several crew members with ties to the destroyed science vessel are experiencing terrifying phenomena of their own. Investigate... at your own risk!
rules:
-- Unique Supply Missions are available during the event. Open the Event to access them.
-- Using Valeo Beta V La'an, any version of B. Crusher, W. Riker, Neelix, Scotty, or Desperate crew will provide a bonus to Supply Missions.
-- Every Supply Mission you complete earns you Event Victory Points. Collect Event Victory Points to unlock Threshold Rewards!
-- Community Rewards are only available during Phase 1. Collect Event Victory Points to unlock these rewards before the phase change!
-- In this event, Squadrons may also compete to advance up the Squadron leaderboards. Join a Squadron to get more rewards!
bonus_text: Crew Bonus: Valeo Beta V La'an, B. Crusher, W. Riker, Neelix, Scotty, or Desperate
rewards_teaser: Reach Rank 1 by gaining Victory Points from Event Supply Missions!

featured_crew.name: Paris
featured_crew.flavor: Fascinated by the study of an alien shuttle that he names Alice, Paris fails to realize he is falling into the vessel’s cunning and dangerous trap.
